title: State employees
author: VD
content_html:
I’m not a big YouTube poster – Joe Namath’s Greatest Moment excepted – but this is pretty funny. Jonah Goldberg rightly cites it as one of the many fundamental dividing points between liberals and libertarians.

It doesn’t quite ring true, of course. The woman is nowhere nearly fat enough.
